{"tid":706782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄現「血天」 網民：921地震前都係咁","createTime":"2018-06-18T07:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T14:29:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7a44051e30ea3cfa3985b117e9ff2c738da34e","tid":706782,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:32:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180618/20424076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424076&d=FFkjnrbNg%2Btm53H1RIhsmU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a34d1494\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424076&h=288759de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180618/20424076</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n高雄現「血天」<br />\n網民：921地震前都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「血染」台灣高雄天空？這是大地震預兆？有網民日前在facebook發佈了一張傍晚時在高雄拍下的照片，相中是一片嚇人的血紅色天空，並問：「各位有看過這麼紅的天嗎？」隨即引發一眾網民熱議，有人甚至擔心是不是天降異象：「當年921前天空也是如此！」所幸後來證實只是虛驚一場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發佈者在fb社團「爆料公社」發文，貼出一張在高雄前鎮拍攝的照片，可以看到是在晚上所拍，巷弄內兩旁的民宅早已熄燈，只剩一盞路燈，而天空卻是一片不尋常的血紅色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民們看到後，紛紛驚訝留言：「921凌晨台中的天空也是紅的」、「921前一晚的天空也是那樣紅」、「921那天我從窗戶看出去的夕陽是紫光」。有人則擔心是不是颱風要來了：「聽說天空越紅，颱風越大是真的嗎」、「老人家說過紅色的天代表有颱風要來」，短短幾小時就累積上百則留言討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來發佈者跟着光源尋找答案，才發現原來紅光是來自「高雄前鎮漁港」，是漁船捕魚時開的聚光燈的光。發佈者隨即向網民們解釋，是因為漁港有新船入海，按照習俗必須要開燈祈求出海捕魚豐收，才會有這一幕。大家看後，都鬆了一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》/三立新聞網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n強國黑心商人慳成本　代糖扮紅糖造饅頭惹致癌風險<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n「澳門商人」騙財$366萬兼騙色　女友聯盟大反擊"},{"pid":"25792918986af0973714ced871988b8dec35ab14","tid":706782,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d857e33ce2729d7a7f610effe060a5a6e7d72b5b","tid":706782,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"震左去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49094a8393b23c3f06def247c8321c2efa6fde9","tid":706782,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"後來發佈者跟着光源尋找答案，才發現原來紅光是來自「高雄前鎮漁港」，是漁船捕魚時開的聚光燈的光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ecc7a1a199b7201988f4337a20a57fada04559","tid":706782,"uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/162141_f54c6eb46eb6a5743c998b6d058a4c8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F162141_f54c6eb46eb6a5743c998b6d058a4c8a.png&h=76e3d4cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a6ac4ffcdef547613baafe4c1e155581f14ffc1","tid":706782,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"26ee063d82eddf54b13ec6bc5d827e9c32704c6d","tid":706782,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a6ac4ffcdef547613baafe4c1e155581f14ffc1","tid":706782,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:52:15.000Z","msg":"kick入去"},{"pid":"465b691eb5f68c0cae1f11062e8092906e86f398","tid":706782,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"第一次衝擊"},{"pid":"211a5ffd8f49173c6341d74f402f89be9d3d3768","tid":706782,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"都on柒尻<br />\n睇到最尾果句即刻此post已完"},{"pid":"e796970a1dd4a2bacdab1932b3c1d53ef244a442","tid":706782,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/222900_15422b4229e4ac1cfb2fb51cbb1c4cce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F222900_15422b4229e4ac1cfb2fb51cbb1c4cce.jpg&h=82110338&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}